articles.title: Four suspected Hamas members arrested in Europe over alleged terrorism plot - CNN
articles.description: Three were arrested in Germany and one in the Netherlands on suspicion of planning attacks on Jewish institutions in Europe, Germany’s federal prosecutor said.
articles.content:
Four alleged Hamas members suspected of plotting terror attacks on European soil have been arrested by German and Dutch authorities, Germanys federal prosecutor said in a statement on Thursday.
